---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<Base title="Tentang Kami — PT Penerbit Quran Indonesia">

<PageHero
  title="Tentang PT Penerbit Quran Indonesia"
  subtitle="Mengenal lebih dekat perusahaan penerbitan buku Islami profesional kami"
  breadcrumb="Tentang Kami"
/>

<section class="py-[88px]">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-7">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-14 items-start">

      <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald to-emerald-light rounded-2xl p-10 flex flex-col justify-between relative overflow-hidden" style="height:400px">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 iso-pattern-white"></div>
        <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col justify-between h-full">
          <div>
            <p class="font-arabic text-white/90 text-[28px] leading-[1.6] mb-4">
              اقْرَأْ بِاسْمِ رَبِّكَ الَّذِي خَلَقَ
            </p>
            <p class="text-white/80 text-sm font-sans italic">
              "Iqra' — Bacalah dengan menyebut nama Tuhanmu"
            </p>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-xs font-sans mt-1">Q.S. Al-'Alaq: 1</p>
          </div>
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full px-4 py-2 w-fit">
            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-gold"></span>
            <span class="text-white text-sm font-semibold font-sans">2024</span>
            <span class="text-white/70 text-xs font-sans">Tahun Berdiri</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div>
        <div class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[.14em] uppercase text-gold flex items-center gap-2.5 mb-5 font-sans">
          <span class="w-7 h-[1.5px] bg-gold"></span>
          Profil Perusahaan
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-[clamp(24px,3vw,34px)] font-black text-surface-6 leading-[1.2] mb-5">
          Menerbitkan Karya Islami <em class="not-italic text-emerald">Berkualitas</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-surface-4 text-[15px] font-sans leading-[1.88] mb-4">
          PT Penerbit Quran Indonesia adalah perusahaan penerbitan buku yang berdiri pada tahun 2024 di Kota Semarang, Jawa Tengah. Kami hadir untuk menjadi mitra terpercaya bagi para penulis muslim Indonesia dalam menerbitkan karya-karya berkualitas tinggi.
        </p>
        <p class="text-surface-4 text-[15px] font-sans leading-[1.88] mb-8">
          Dengan komitmen pada standar profesional dan nilai-nilai keislaman, kami menyediakan layanan penerbitan lengkap dari proses naskah hingga distribusi buku ke seluruh Indonesia.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-8">
          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-emerald pl-5 py-2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-6 text-sm mb-1">Visi</h3>
            <p class="text-surface-4 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8]">
              Menjadi penerbit buku Islami terkemuka yang menginspirasi dan mencerdaskan umat melalui karya-karya bermutu tinggi.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-emerald pl-5 py-2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-6 text-sm mb-1">Misi</h3>
            <ul class="text-surface-4 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8] list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
              <li>Menerbitkan buku-buku Islami berkualitas dengan standar profesional</li>
              <li>Mendukung penulis muslim Indonesia dalam berkarya</li>
              <li>Mendistribusikan karya Islami ke seluruh nusantara</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-emerald pl-5 py-2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-surface-6 text-sm mb-1">Nilai</h3>
            <p class="text-surface-4 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8]">
              Amanah, Profesional, Berkualitas, dan Bermanfaat bagi umat.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="py-[88px] bg-surface-1">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-7">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <div class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[.14em] uppercase text-gold flex items-center justify-center gap-2.5 mb-4 font-sans">
        <span class="w-7 h-[1.5px] bg-gold"></span>
        Data Perusahaan
        <span class="w-7 h-[1.5px] bg-gold"></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-[clamp(24px,3vw,34px)] font-black text-surface-6 leading-[1.2]">
        Identitas & Legalitas Usaha
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-surface-2/50">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-surface-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-sans mb-2">Nama Perusahaan</p>
        <p class="text-surface-6 font-bold text-sm">PT Penerbit Quran Indonesia</p>
        <p class="text-surface-4 text-xs font-sans mt-0.5">(PT)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-surface-2/50">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-surface-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-sans mb-2">Tahun Berdiri</p>
        <p class="text-surface-6 font-bold text-sm">2024</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-surface-2/50">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-surface-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-sans mb-2">Bentuk Badan Usaha</p>
        <p class="text-surface-6 font-bold text-sm">Perseroan Terbatas (PT)</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-surface-2/50">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-surface-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-sans mb-2">Domisili</p>
        <p class="text-surface-6 font-bold text-sm">Kota Semarang</p>
        <p class="text-surface-4 text-xs font-sans mt-0.5">Jawa Tengah 50115</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-surface-2/50">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-surface-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-sans mb-2">Bidang Usaha</p>
        <p class="text-surface-6 font-bold text-sm">Penerbitan Buku</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-surface-2/50">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-surface-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-sans mb-2">Website</p>
        <a href="https://penerbitquran.com" class="text-emerald font-bold text-sm hover:text-emerald-light transition-colors">penerbitquran.com</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-surface-2/50">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-surface-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-sans mb-2">Email</p>
        <a href="mailto:penerbitquranindonesia@gmail.com" class="text-emerald font-bold text-[13px] hover:text-emerald-light transition-colors break-all">penerbitquranindonesia@gmail.com</a>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-5 border border-surface-2/50">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-semibold text-surface-4 uppercase tracking-wider font-sans mb-2">WhatsApp</p>
        <a href="https://wa.me/6282136741135" class="text-emerald font-bold text-sm hover:text-emerald-light transition-colors">0821-3674-1135</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald to-emerald-light rounded-2xl overflow-hidden relative">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 iso-pattern-white"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 p-8">
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lg">📍</span>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Alamat Kantor</h3>
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/85 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8]">
            Jl. Ngablak Indah II No.24A, RT 008/RW 004,<br>
            Kel. Bangetayu Kulon, Kec. Genuk,<br>
            Kota Semarang, Jawa Tengah 50115
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="text-lg">🕐</span>
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Jam Operasional</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="text-white/85 text-[13px] font-sans leading-[1.8] space-y-0.5">
            <p>Sen–Kam: 08.00–16.00</p>
            <p>Jum: 08.00–17.00</p>
            <p>Sab: 08.00–15.00</p>
            <p class="text-white/50">Ahad & Hari Libur: Tutup</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>
